title: Grateful Dead Live at Carrier Dome, Syracuse U on 1982-09-24
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Friend Of The Devil-> CC Rider, Ramble On Rose, Minglewood Blues, Bird Song-> Looks Like Rain, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Far From Me-> Playin' In The Band-> Crazy Fingers-> Throwing Stones-> Drums-> Iko Iko-> Truckin'-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Brokedown Palace
